MCU communication manager daemon

Description:
    MCU communication manager daemon provides the mechanism to communicate with MCU

Input parameters:
    --dev|-d        - serial device name to communicate with MCU. Default is /dev/ser3

Usage:
    mcu_com [OPTION]

Examples:
    mcu_com
    mcu_com --dev=/dev/ser4
    mcu_com -d /dev/ser4

